"dr-xr-xr-x. 2 root root 4096 2014-11-23 11-23 03:13 bin\n"
"dr-xr-xr-x. 5 root root 1024 2014-11-23 11-23 05:29 boot\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:595
msgid "Add the _trailing slash_ to the end of folders:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:598
msgid ""
"By default, the `ls` command does not display the last slash of a folder.  "
"In some cases, like for scripts for example, it is useful to display them:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (bash)
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:599
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ ls -dF /etc\n"
"/etc/\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:605
msgid "Hide some extensions:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Fenced code block (bash)
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:606
#, no-wrap
