msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:1482
#, no-wrap
msgid "    Special care must be taken when using aliases which can be potentially dangerous! For example, an alias set up without the administrator's knowledge:\n"
