#, no-wrap
msgid "ls is an alias to Â« ls -rt Â»\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:1516
msgid ""
"Now that this is known, we can see the results of using the alias or "
"disabling it one time with the `\\` by executing the following:"
